%% E050 - EnrichmentWorker flow - F1-4 Pipeline
%% Source: docs/design/f1-4-enrichment.md (E048), docs/design/f1-4-prompts.md (E049)
flowchart TB
    Start([Receive EnrichmentMessage]) --> SelectStrategy{Select strategy by sourceId}
    SelectStrategy -->|sourceId=1| CsjnStrategy[CsjnEnrichmentStrategy]
    SelectStrategy -->|sourceId=2,3,4| FullStrategy[FullEnrichmentStrategy]
    CsjnStrategy --> CheckJudges{missingFields contains judges?}
    CheckJudges -->|Yes| CallJudges[JudgesExtractionPrompt]
    CallJudges --> ValidateJudges{Valid JSON?}
    ValidateJudges -->|No| RetryOrFail[Retry or DLQ]
    ValidateJudges -->|Yes| CheckStatutes{missingFields contains cited_statutes?}
    CheckJudges -->|No| CheckStatutes
    CheckStatutes -->|Yes| CallStatutes[StatutesExtractionPrompt]
    CallStatutes --> ValidateStatutes{Valid JSON?}
    ValidateStatutes -->|No| RetryOrFail
    ValidateStatutes -->|Yes| CheckCitationTypes{missingFields contains citation_types?}
    CheckStatutes -->|No| CheckCitationTypes
    CheckCitationTypes -->|Yes| CallCitationTypes[CitationTypePrompt]
    CallCitationTypes --> ValidateCitationTypes{Valid JSON?}
    ValidateCitationTypes -->|No| RetryOrFail
    ValidateCitationTypes -->|Yes| Merge[Merge extractedMetadata + GPT outputs]
    CheckCitationTypes -->|No| Merge
    Merge --> Chunk[Chunk normalizedText]
    Chunk --> BuildMessage[Build IndexerMessage]
    BuildMessage --> Publish[Publish to queue-indexer]
    Publish --> End([End])
    FullStrategy --> FullPrompt[FullEnrichmentPrompt]
    FullPrompt --> Merge
    RetryOrFail --> EndFail([End - failed])
